  "body": "As part of #479 `engine_preparePayload` should be assembling a block for proposal ahead of the call of this method.  Rather than assembling a block at call time, `engine_getPayload` should instead use the candidate block from `engine_preparePayload`\n\nacceptance criteria:\n`engine_getPayload` should:\n\n* interrupt any running block proposal worker\n* immediately return the best pre-prepared candidate block \n  * if candidate block is unavailable, return an empty block\n  * free the candidate block storage",
